<A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=50027">My Profile</a></center></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utojizimitz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tojizimitz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/24/01 4:20:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's up with Venril?</span><hr size=1> Hey Arant, I am on Karana too and looking at my 10th trip to VS.  First 9 - No Staff <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarantrunemaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arant Runemaster</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://verbalsabre.50megs.com/images/cooked.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/27/01 6:54:24 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's up with Venril?</span><hr size=1> We just having bad luck or is he rarer than I think? <p><font color="#ff0000">
<center><b>55th Evoker of Karana<b></p>
<A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=50027">My Profile</a></center></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucachevonnukenstein.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cache Von Nukenstein</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/27/01 9:06:35 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's up with Venril?</span><hr size=1> It is definately rarer than it used to be... took me 7 times to get him to drop it.  I think VI changed this when they upped the drop rate on Phinny, who seems to have the BCS every 8th time or so instead of every 15-20th time.  Making it an, at the very least, uncommon drop makes the epic a lot harder when VS is on a rotation or, like on Xev, European guilds kill him during the U.S. workday.  Good luck to you, when you get your epic it will all be worth it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
