57th Evoker of Bristlebane<br><a href=http://www.circleoflegends.org>Circle of Legends</a>
<a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=79999>profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyaldin111.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yaldin111</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/31/01 6:14:34 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's up with Venril?</span><hr size=1> Also on Karana (as you know Arant) he didn't drop it the first time my guild was up for him and we're gonna be up again round the end of january....hope to god this is it for me since I've had phinny staff and gabstik for well over 3 months and VS is supposed to be the EASY step (I know a hundred wizards with gabstik and gnarled but no BCS /sigh) I'm up for it too from now on....the curse of VS!!<br>
